'''普列卡維察'''（{{lang-sr|пљескавица}}, {{lang-mk|плескавица}}) 是一種流行在[[巴爾幹|巴爾幹]]地區的菜餚，為由各種不同類型肉餡製成的肉餅<ref name="KittlerSucher2011">{{cite book|author1=Pamela Goyan Kittler|author2=Kathryn P. Sucher|author3=Marcia Nahikian-Nelms|title=Food and Culture, 6th ed.|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=R06H7WabJuMC&pg=PA410|date=August 2011|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=978-0-538-73497-4|page=410|quote=Large, thin meat patties made from lamb and beef, known as pljeskavica, are considered a popular dish in Bosnia , Croatia and Serbia.|access-date=2015-12-27|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030025946/https://books.google.com/books?id=R06H7WabJuMC&pg=PA410|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

普列卡維察是[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]的國菜<ref name="KittlerSucher2011"/>，在波赫、[[克羅埃西亞|克羅埃西亞]]、[[蒙特內哥羅|蒙特內哥羅]]、[[馬其頓|馬其頓]]也很流行，並且在[[羅馬尼亞|羅馬尼亞]]、[[斯洛維尼亞|斯洛維尼亞]]、[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]也能發現<ref name="Seierstad2006">{{cite book|author=Asne Seierstad|title=With Their Backs to the World: Portraits from Serbia|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=S6kdxZABmnkC&pg=PA111|date=7 November 2006|publisher=Basic Books|isbn=978-0-7867-2243-3|page=111|quote=...pljeskavica – a flat cake of ground meat and spices.|access-date=2015-12-27|archive-date=2013-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228124359/http://books.google.com/books?id=S6kdxZABmnkC&pg=PA111|dead-url=no}}</ref>。現在普列卡維察正普及至歐洲其他地區。

